Name: Squaxel
About the game: Squaxel is a sandbox game in which you will be able to visit multiple flying islands. You can build on them, destroy them and talk to the people on them. You also have your own island to experiment! Features: - Building your own island - Do quests - Explore islands - Destroy whatever you want
